00:00:44.591 --> 00:00:46.518
We impose house style.

00:00:46.542 --> 00:00:49.228
Every publication has a house style.

00:00:49.252 --> 00:00:51.775
The New Yorker's
is particularly distinctive.

00:00:52.503 --> 00:00:55.283
We sometimes get teased for our style.

00:00:55.307 --> 00:00:59.647
Imagine -- we still spell
"teen-ager" with a hyphen,

00:00:59.671 --> 00:01:01.947
